{"tid":1444391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反省下點解沙田我地會嬴，我支持人海戰術硬碰硬","createTime":"2019-08-11T12:20:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T13:51:24.000Z","uid":65700,"like":67,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1d12a1305339273c4facbfa72911e4370647b0e3","tid":1444391,"uid":65700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:20:10.000Z","msg":"沙田開打,其實係因為走唔切, 走唔到, 焗住要打<br />\n我地人數多佢地咁多, 佢地一個打到幾多個??基本上要2-3隻狗先捉到一個人<br />\n成日話裝備唔夠抽, 我唔同意, 除非佢地開槍掃射, 你一碌棍可以打到幾多人<br />\n如果同狗用人海戰術硬碰硬, 真係會輸咩?<br />\n宜家打遊撃變左無人數優勢不停俾狗捉, 咁樣落去我見唔到希望<br />\n再者我覺得打遊撃政府都係唔會理你<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我覺得應該要擊退警察,令到高官感受到人生受到威脅</span></span>,先會迫到佢地去解決問題<br />\n<br />\n受傷?我預左<br />\n本民前當年魚革有晒榜樣俾大家<br />\n希望大家慢慢衝破心理關口<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果我係三毛, 死全家</span></span>"},{"pid":"d80534fad1d00b4dbe30af137ce9c11c8b75e39e","tid":1444391,"uid":65700,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:22:00.000Z","msg":"三毛, 死全家"},{"pid":"dbf424076683bb0ae4958b27dc2231b790e4dec2","tid":1444391,"uid":65700,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:22:18.000Z","msg":"三毛, 死全家"},{"pid":"b16137cdd2b0089eda0c87aed131aeb8892e8b1f","tid":1444391,"uid":65700,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:22:56.000Z","msg":"三毛, 死全家"},{"pid":"12489f29766c22d007ab911b4edea16e7c509ee5","tid":1444391,"uid":65700,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:23:26.000Z","msg":"三毛, 死全家"},{"pid":"22e40e5254db0199c3c0f4ec6f28eaa98573452f","tid":1444391,"uid":96704,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:24:11.000Z","msg":"新城市有高低地形優勢<br />\n你兩邊一條馬路大直路點夠打"},{"pid":"859ba7c4ce23d9dcef81dc3c9a0af289f60e1b00","tid":1444391,"uid":64345,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:25:17.000Z","msg":"冷氣軍師<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\